OL,3,C'It made me absolutely livid' Mary
OL,4,CNightingale on being deepfaked
OL,6,FITV News journalist and presenter Mary
OL,7,FNightingale has spoken of how outraged
OL,8,Fshe was to discover she had been a
OL,9,Fvictim of a deep fake last month.
OL,11,FA manipulated version of the news
OL,12,Fanchor appeared on social media in
OL,13,FFebruary before it was deleted.
OL,15,FThe video, which lasted around 45
OL,16,Fseconds, showed Nightingale sitting at
OL,17,Fher desk in an ITV studio as if
OL,18,Fpresenting the ITV Evening News.
