OL,3,C'It made me absolutely livid' Mary
OL,4,CNightingale on being deepfaked
OL,6,FHowever, it then went on to promote a
OL,7,Ftype of investment app in which singer
OL,8,FDua Lipa was also deepfaked.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru's Wales This
OL,11,FWeek programme, Nightingale said: "It
OL,12,Fmade me absolutely livid.
OL,14,F"For someone to take my image and
OL,15,Fsupposedly my voice and manipulate it
OL,16,Fin that way, it's theft, it's identity
OL,17,Ftheft."
