OL,3,C'It made me absolutely livid' Mary
OL,4,CNightingale on being deepfaked
OL,6,FDeepfake videos and pictures have
OL,7,Fbecome more common as generative
OL,8,FArtificial Intelligence (AI) tools
OL,9,Fbecome more widespread and accessible.
OL,11,FAs many as 500,000 appeared online
OL,12,Flast year, and fake celebrity
OL,13,Fendorsements are also becoming more
OL,14,Fcommon.
OL,16,FIn the UK, news broadcasters adhere to
OL,17,Fstrict rules that limit their ability
OL,18,Fto promote products, espeicially while
OL,19,Fon air.
