OL,3,C'It made me absolutely livid' Mary
OL,4,CNightingale on being deepfaked
OL,6,FWith elections in both the UK and USA
OL,7,Flater this year, there are also fears
OL,8,Fthey could be used to spread
OL,9,Fdisinformation.
OL,11,F"I looked at it with my husband and he
OL,12,Fsaid 'okay I know it's not you' but
OL,13,Fanyone who didn't know it wasn't me
OL,14,Fwould actually find it quite
OL,15,Fconvincing," Nightingale continued.
OL,17,F"In our job, trust is everything. If
OL,18,Fpeople don't trust you, you cannot
OL,19,Feffectively do your job.
