OL,3,C'It made me absolutely livid' Mary
OL,4,CNightingale on being deepfaked
OL,6,F"If people start to doubt my
OL,7,Fcredibility, if people start to think
OL,8,F'oh she would say that, she flogs
OL,9,Fdodgy investment deals, then that
OL,10,Freally does start to eat away at my
OL,11,Fprofessional credibility."
OL,13,FThe developments of AI technologies,
OL,14,Fespecially those known as machine
OL,15,Flearning - where machines learn from
OL,16,Ftheir own actions - have caused many
OL,17,Fpeople to worry about the AI becoming
OL,18,Ftoo powerful.
