OL,3,C'It made me absolutely livid' Mary
OL,4,CNightingale on being deepfaked
OL,6,FHowever, Professor Matt Jones from
OL,7,FSwansea University's department of
OL,8,Fcomputer science believes it's
OL,9,Fdeepfakes and sinister uses that
OL,10,Fpresent the most tangible and
OL,11,Fimmediate dangers.
OL,13,F"Deepfakes is one of the problems that
OL,14,Fwe should address," he said.
OL,16,F"There's a great deal of worry about
OL,17,FAI becoming our overlords, becoming
OL,18,Fsentient, but I actually think that's
OL,19,Fa smokescreen.
