OL,3,C'It made me absolutely livid' Mary
OL,4,CNightingale on being deepfaked
OL,6,F"What we need to worry about is people
OL,7,Fusing things like deepfakes to
OL,8,Fmanipulate elections or to scam you
OL,9,Fout of your money.
OL,11,F"We should focus on those near and
OL,12,Fpresent dangers and not get carried
OL,13,Faway worrying about Sci-Fi visions of
OL,14,Fsentient AI."
OL,16,FTrade unions and campaigners have
OL,17,Fcalled for stronger legislation and
OL,18,Fregulation on AI and its uses.
